    "roleHeading": "Article",
    "title": "Configuring Maps support"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "An iOS app that’s able to display point-to-point directions can register as a",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "routing app and make those directions available to Maps along with all other",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "apps on a user’s device. Registering as a routing app improves the user",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "experience because other apps can access your app’s routing information,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "and these apps don’t need to provide their own routing directions. Because Maps",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "displays apps in the App Store that provide directions, registering your iOS",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "app as a routing app is a great way to let users know about it.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A routing app provides specific directions in addition to what Maps supports,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "such as subway routes, hiking trails, and bike paths. Before you can select the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "routing modes that your app supports, follow the steps in",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/adding-capabilities-to-your-app#Add-a-capability",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " to add the Maps",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "capability to your app’s target.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "maps",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "This capability is only applicable to custom routing apps on iOS. You",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "don’t need to add the Maps capability to a macOS app to be able to use the",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "MapKit framework.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Note",
          "style": "note",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Select-the-supported-routing-modes",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Select the supported routing modes",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Before the system can distribute requests for directions to your routing app,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "you must inform it of the routing modes your app supports by following these",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "\n",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "steps:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Select your project in Xcode’s Project navigator.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Select the app’s target from the Targets list.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Click the Signing & Capabilities tab in the project editor.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Find the Maps capability.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Select the relevant routing modes by checking the corresponding checkboxes.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "routing-modes",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Xcode adds the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/BundleResources/Information-Property-List/MKDirectionsApplicationSupportedModes",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": "",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "array to your app’s ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "Info.plist",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " file (if not already present) and uses the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "modes you select to populate the array with the necessary values.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "After you select the necessary routing modes, there are additional",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "configuration steps you must complete before your app can start providing",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "point-to-point directions, such as specifying a directions request document",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "type and declaring your app’s geographic region. For more information,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/library/archive/documentation/UserExperience/Conceptual/LocationAwarenessPG/ProvidingDirections/ProvidingDirections.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/TP40009497-CH8-SW8",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
